sellerCard.oneLiner: BuilderAll, ClickFunnels, Wix and ChatBot Expert
sellerCard.description: Hi, I'm Shaekh. Since 2018, I have been working as a Web/funnel Developer. and have working experience in Clickfunnels, BuilderAll, Wix, LeadPages, SquareSpace, Kajabi & Chatbot. Specially use these platform for building Landing Page, Sales Funnel, Membership Funnel, Automated Webinar or Full website. I will make you happy with my work not punch line. So if you want that extra creativity in your project, your search ends right here.

description.content:
If you are looking for an experienced funnel expert to develop or design your funnel/website pages using revolutionary Clickfunnels, your search ends right here.


I have been working on ClickFunnels since 2018 and I am helping you in setting up your most powerful website/funnels with a great conversion rate, you have just gotten a one-stop solution that will be more than your need.


I can help you with the following:

  • Landing Page
  • Squeeze/ Opt-in/ Lead Generation Funnel
  • Sales/Membership/Webinar Funnel
  • Product Launching Funnel
  • Video/ Long Form Sales Pages
  • Order Forms with Custom Features (Highlight products, Multiple Payment Option, Promo Code, Purchase Pixel Events, etc)
  • Upsell/ Downsell Pages
  • Payment, Domain, Zapier, and Cloudflare integration
  • Autoresponder integration and Email Campaigns with Mailchimp, Active Campaign, Aweber, Get Response, Clickfunnels Actionetics, etc.


*** 100% money back guaranty & 100 % Satisfaction ***


You will love to work with my service and trust me, for the next time you will confidently contact me for any kind of technical support.


Thank you for your valuable time. and look forward to working with you soon.
